<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Storage Price Estimator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h2 class="text-center">Algorand Storage Price Estimator</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <form id="uploadForm" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="file" class="form-label">Select File to Estimate Storage Cost</label>
                                <input type="file" class="form-control" id="file" name="file" required>
                                <div id="fileHelp" class="form-text">Select any file to calculate the storage cost on Algorand.</div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="mb-3 form-check">
                                <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="isPermanent" name="isPermanent">
                                <label class="form-check-label" for="isPermanent">Permanent Storage (Added to Renewal Pool)</label>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <h5>Parametri di Prezzo Personalizzati</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Modifica questi parametri per vedere come influenzano il costo di archiviazione in tempo reale.</p>
                                
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="basePrice" class="form-label d-flex justify-content-between">
                                        <span>Prezzo Base (microAlgos):</span>
                                        <span id="basePriceValue"><%= defaultBasePrice %></span>
                                    </label>
                                    <input type="range" class="form-range" id="basePrice" name="basePrice" 
                                        min="100000" max="500000" step="10000" value="<%= defaultBasePrice %>">
                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between small text-muted">
                                        <span>100,000 (0.1 Algos)</span>
                                        <span>500,000 (0.5 Algos)</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="bytePrice" class="form-label d-flex justify-content-between">
                                        <span>Prezzo per KB (microAlgos):</span>
                                        <span id="bytePriceValue"><%= defaultBytePrice %></span>
                                    </label>
                                    <input type="range" class="form-range" id="bytePrice" name="bytePrice" 
                                        min="50" max="200" step="5" value="<%= defaultBytePrice %>">
                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between small text-muted">
                                        <span>50</span>
                                        <span>200</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Calculate Price</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                        
                        <div id="results" class="mt-4" style="display: none;">
                            <div class="alert alert-info">
                                <h4 class="alert-heading">Price Estimation Results</h4>
                                <hr>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>File Size:</strong> <span id="fileSize"></span></p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>Storage Type:</strong> <span id="storageType"></span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row mt-2">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>Price (microAlgos):</strong> <span id="priceInMicroAlgos"></span></p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>Price (Algos):</strong> <span id="priceInAlgos"></span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr>
                                <h5>Dettaglio Calcolo</h5>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>Dimensione in KB:</strong> <span id="sizeInKB"></span></p>
                                        <p><strong>Prezzo Base:</strong> <span id="basePriceResult"></span> microAlgos</p>
                                        <p><strong>Costo per KB:</strong> <span id="bytePrice"></span> microAlgos</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <p><strong>Costo Totale Byte:</strong> <span id="byteCost"></span> microAlgos</p>
                                        <p><strong>Prezzo Base + Byte:</strong> <span id="baseTotal"></span> microAlgos</p>
                                        <p><strong>Moltiplicatore Permanente:</strong> <span id="permanentMultiplier"></span>x</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div id="error" class="mt-4 alert alert-danger" style="display: none;">
                            <h4 class="alert-heading">Error</h4>
                            <hr>
                            <p id="errorMessage"></p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div id="loading" class="text-center mt-4" style="display: none;">
                            <div class="spinner-border text-primary" role="status">
                                <span class="visually-hidden">Loading...</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mt-2">Calculating storage price...</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4 alert alert-secondary">
                            <h5>Nota sui Costi di Archiviazione</h5>
                            <p>I costi di archiviazione mostrati sono stime e possono variare in base a diversi fattori:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Dimensione del file:</strong> Il costo aumenta linearmente con la dimensione in KB.</li>
                                <li><strong>Tipo di archiviazione:</strong> L'archiviazione permanente ha un moltiplicatore di 5x rispetto a quella temporanea.</li>
                                <li><strong>Prezzo base:</strong> Un costo fisso applicato a ogni transazione indipendentemente dalla dimensione del file.</li>
                                <li><strong>Prezzo per KB:</strong> Il costo variabile per kilobyte di dati.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p class="mb-1">In un ambiente di produzione, i costi potrebbero essere influenzati anche da:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Condizioni di mercato della rete Algorand</li>
                                <li>Modifiche ai parametri del contratto smart</li>
                                <li>Disponibilit√† dei nodi di archiviazione</li>
                                <li>Durata dell'archiviazione</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p class="mt-2 small text-muted"><strong>Formula di calcolo:</strong> basePrice + (sizeInKB * bytePrice) * [permanentMultiplier se permanente]</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 